 23→Although prior works have explored building instruction tuning data for tool use~\citep{li2023api,patil2023gorilla,tang2023toolalpaca,xu2023tool}, they fail to fully stimulate the tool-use capabilities within LLMs and have inherent limitations: (1) \textbf{limited APIs}: they either fail to involve real-world APIs (e.g., RESTAPI)~\citep{patil2023gorilla,tang2023toolalpaca} or consider only a small scope of APIs with poor diversity~\citep{patil2023gorilla,xu2023tool,li2023api};
